## INPUT

```
Project: Horizon Platform Migration
Context: Q3 release — target go-live 31 July. Exec sponsor gets weekly update.

Update notes (week ending 14 June):

Completed this week:
- Data migration scripts for Phase 1 (customer records) signed off and ready for UAT
- Infra provisioning in staging env complete
- Security review for auth module passed

In progress:
- UAT for Phase 1 underway — 3 of 9 test scenarios complete, no defects yet
- Phase 2 (transaction history) still in development — team says "on track" but
