Dependencies:
- Client sign-off on data schema (outstanding from last week, now overdue by 5 days)
- Legal team approval of data retention policy — requested 3 weeks ago, no response

Metrics:
- 18 of 45 total tasks complete (40%)
- 2 items moved from "done" back to "in progress" after QA found issues

Other:
- Team lead flagged that if vendor extract is not received by 20 June,
